mlx.data.core.CharTrie.insert

CharTrie.insert(self: mlx.data._c.core.CharTrie, token: Union[str, List[str]]) → mlx.data._c.core.CharTrieNode

Insert a token in the trie making a new token if it doesn’t already exist.

Parameters

token (str or list[char]) – The new token to be inserted given either as a string or a list of characters.
